Application to track run times built using Spring REST APIs and AngularJS front end.

The application runs on Spring boot with embedded Tomcat server. The application uses spring-data-jpa to connect to MySQL database to deliver data.

The application uses JSON web token as a mechanism to authenticate in a purely stateless and secure manner.

Building the application:

./gradlew clean build

Running the application server:

java -jar build/libs/jogLog-0.1.0.jar

Accessing the application:

https://localhost:8443/

Swagger UI for API reference:

https://localhost:8443/swagger-ui.html
